data.description: Welcome home to Deerfield, a prime location in the heart of Jacksonville. This splendid home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a captivating open floor plan complemented by graceful, vaulted ceilings. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting ample cabinet and counter space, as well as top-of-the-line stainless-steel appliances.Outside, a spacious yard and a convenient one-car garage enhance the property's appeal.Benefit from the home's strategic location, just minutes away from MCB Camp LeJeune and MCAS New River, with a plethora of new shopping, dining, and leisure options nearby. Furthermore, you'll appreciate the absence of city taxes.Don't delay - request a showing promptly to seize the opportunity to view this home before it follows the trend of other exceptional properties in Onslow County by being taken off the market. This competitively priced home will not remain available for long!
